  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347280/extras/3e6c2f8a511d526e741d6cda8636d11d.webp?t=1741883156\" width=600 height=40 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347280/extras/3be66942e6b81ccd4c3a250571a66356.poster.avif?t=1741883156\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347280/extras/3be66942e6b81ccd4c3a250571a66356.webm?t=1741883156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347280/extras/3be66942e6b81ccd4c3a250571a66356.mp4?t=1741883156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Push your King forward to play your cards on the front lines. Stockpile your Power to afford expensive and powerful units like the Queen and Cannon.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347280/extras/4ef8fa58cbe2d29cf97bf1733f518aac.webp?t=1741883156\" width=600 height=40 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347280/extras/38b121b0a7fcaef6bcdf7173ee86bbf8.poster.avif?t=1741883156\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347280/extras/38b121b0a7fcaef6bcdf7173ee86bbf8.webm?t=1741883156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347280/extras/38b121b0a7fcaef6bcdf7173ee86bbf8.mp4?t=1741883156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Draft new cards, upgrade your Ruler, and choose powerful gambits to create game-breaking synergies. Build your deck YOUR way and master 4 unique Factions to become the ultimate champion.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347280/extras/4a904044879a574ccfd8c68249c15dc2.webp?t=1741883156\" width=600 height=40 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347280/extras/4b08328c0b67a93a2c07efe4e533c9c5.poster.avif?t=1741883156\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347280/extras/4b08328c0b67a93a2c07efe4e533c9c5.webm?t=1741883156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347280/extras/4b08328c0b67a93a2c07efe4e533c9c5.mp4?t=1741883156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>One well-placed unit is the difference between victory and defeat. Place new units to counterattack your enemy and swing the battle in your favor. Master your strategy to defeat 13 unique bosses.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347280/extras/330123959886b36f719bc5c2ad6d3c76.webp?t=1741883156\" width=600 height=40 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347280/extras/273c0ee042fdb856fc936204cfc37ddb.poster.avif?t=1741883156\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347280/extras/273c0ee042fdb856fc936204cfc37ddb.webm?t=1741883156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347280/extras/273c0ee042fdb856fc936204cfc37ddb.mp4?t=1741883156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Defeat t